Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:15.07,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}就算最终无人倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:21.50,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}这也是我最真诚的光之祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:27.14,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}我才明白直面自我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.99,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}就能变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:33.75,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}不要放过这每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.55,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}在迷茫与彷徨中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:39.82,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}不断战胜无数个日夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:44.14,OP2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\shad2.4\1a&HFE&\blur3}在这幸存的世界里
